{"tid":164226,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"「先進」的北京公廁　人臉識別防取大量廁紙","createTime":"2017-03-20T13:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T17:14:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ede050fe2134aaa77378c7b4f9416be238dba9","tid":164226,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"中國不少人欠缺公德心，經常於公廁偷廁紙取回家自用。北京天壇公園公廁自2007年推出免費廁紙服務以來，經常出現過量取廁紙問題。為杜絕相關行為，公園裝設共6個「黑盒型」人臉識別系統廁紙機，紀錄人臉以限制每人取紙量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/toilet_paper-694x390.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Ftoilet_paper-694x390.png&h=b1545103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F1B.jpg&h=f7bd3b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據新京報報導，天壇公園內人流最多的廁所，每天得換20卷廁紙，平均不到半小時就得更換一次，主因有許多人經常過量取紙，甚至會整卷取走，工作人員曾試圖大力勸止但不果。公園負責人表示，免費廁紙服務推出至今已十年，園區早已發現這種缺德行為，惟天壇公園算是北京的門面之一，故一直未有取消免費廁紙服務，但亦因未有相關法律管制過量取紙行為，所以園區一直得想方設法務求解決問題。<br />\n這6個「黑盒」分別裝設於園內南、西及北門公廁，市民可站在特定的感應區前，「黑盒」便會通過屏幕辨識人臉及紀錄，數秒後便會出紙。機器一次只會提供60厘米廁紙，如同一人要相隔9分鐘才能再取一次廁紙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/7B-694x474.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F7B-694x474.jpg&h=afde6864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公園負責人指，裝設「黑盒」後，廁紙用量明顯下降，初步能夠發揮預期效果。但亦發現「黑盒」給紙速度頗慢，人流多時應付不來導致大排長龍，像是人流最多的北門廁所，兩台機器都被弄壞，所以又暫時停用了。但園區仍會繼續觀察及研究，務求找出一個最適合的方法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/20/beijingtoilet/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2Fbeijingtoilet%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX55UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=bffec83a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/20/beijingtoilet/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"a4e8ce9657c2a87c0d12b4628c09de79a076a117","tid":164226,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"門口賣面具"},{"pid":"9035fd2e0bf663691175a5cc38e8b9ee7352e6aa","tid":164226,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門口賣面具</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04cc9e6a0f0588b34573ec68745ddbd7c3632b6","tid":164226,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>門口賣面具</blockquote><br />\n變面神器?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"81b91096135b47cd77ce169444fc3572b02e0b98","tid":164226,"uid":60428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"淘寶賣人面相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb16ae7e48de6f688f6753cc301fc4411e2b716","tid":164226,"uid":70962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"大陸咩都收費先可以度絕貪心狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前口開士多賣廁紙咪得囉，搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192251a6dfaa5f4fc9df3358e887d854871678f9","tid":164226,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"兩台機器都被弄壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989674b4f499457fc5deb201be05d22236b2e200","tid":164226,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6101556a2ffd224717534448c99fbd5e484b9e18","tid":164226,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"支那人： 不怕被偷嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92deea5ef1172477fc19ac1801f75eec